00:54:59.828 --> 00:55:16.475
Believe God for big; stop believing for small. Thank You, Lord, that we have protection concerning viruses.

00:55:16.476 --> 00:55:37.435
We call that virus down in Jesus'name. We have the authority of the believer.

00:55:37.436 --> 00:55:46.440
A thousand shall fall at our side and ten thousand at our right hand, but nothing shall come nigh us.

00:55:46.441 --> 00:55:59.071
We'll not be afraid of any kind of pestilence or plagues. Jesus dwells on the inside of us.

00:55:59.072 --> 00:56:04.862
Who is this uncircumcised Philistine that he tries to defy the armies of the Lord?

00:56:04.863 --> 00:56:14.575
Concerning disease, plagues, cancers, and diabetes—who is this uncircumcised Philistine?

00:56:14.576 --> 00:56:52.913
Jehovah Jireh dwells on the inside of me. I lack no good thing.

00:56:52.914 --> 00:57:19.999
I renew my mind from stinking thinking today. We resist the devil and he must flee.

00:57:20.000 --> 00:57:50.773
Folks, you've got to be like a bulldog on a bone. "You are not going to steal from me anymore, devil!"Stand up on the inside.

00:57:50.774 --> 00:58:15.795
The waves try to knock you down, but I keep standing. I'm not moved by what I see or feel; I'm moved by what the word of God says. How bad do you want change?

00:58:15.796 --> 00:58:46.950
When you get some grit down inside you—"I will not be moved by this anymore!"When the police say your kid did something bad again—no, my child is turning around.

00:58:46.952 --> 00:58:57.559
I call him saved and delivered. I refuse to be moved by circumstances.

00:58:57.560 --> 00:59:29.675
My daughter is overcoming; she's healed and whole. When the doctor gives a bad report, I'm not moved by what I see.

00:59:29.676 --> 00:59:45.441
With His stripes, I am healed. The word is my foundation. I stagger not at the promise of God through unbelief.

00:59:45.442 --> 01:00:16.000
I am not moved by the report of the doctor. I will live a long life and declare the works of the Lord.

01:00:16.001 --> 01:00:44.333
He said He would satisfy me with long life, and I'm not satisfied yet.

01:00:44.334 --> 01:01:18.041
I hope this blessed you today. That's how you live by faith. Lean on Him and be confident in Him.

01:01:18.042 --> 01:01:39.356
He gives us a garment of praise for a spirit of heaviness. Worship Him in spirit and in truth today.

01:01:39.358 --> 01:01:51.562
My son said an hour and eight minutes. We'll do more prayer videos.

01:01:51.563 --> 01:02:06.892
Let's think bigger. God wants to use everybody, and we're in the end here.

01:02:06.893 --> 01:02:11.999
If you're new here, subscribe and click the notification bell.

01:02:12.000 --> 01:02:38.514
We pray for President Trump for special covering. Cover his mind and body.

01:02:38.515 --> 01:03:05.972
Thank You for President Trump today—that he will release the wealth from the deep for the body of Christ.

01:03:05.973 --> 01:03:18.559
Put a smile on your face and a song in your heart. Jesus loves you and we love you. God bless you all, and we'll see you again soon. Bye-bye.

